{"tid":1010811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"數碼港海面女子遇溺　送院死亡","createTime":"2019-02-06T09:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T09:21:11.000Z","uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"feb93ab2c83b5365d10e7e4fab331b335fe43c4d","tid":1010811,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"數碼港污水處理廠對出海面，今早(6日)11時39分，一名年約50歲女子被發現在海中載浮載沉，水警及消防趕至，將女子救起，當時已陷入昏迷，立即由救護車送院搶救，惜告返魂乏術。警方到場調查，在女事主身上檢獲財物，正追查其身份以及墮海原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190206/bkn-20190206121210727-0206_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190206%2Fbkn-20190206121210727-0206_00822_001.html&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTHs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=d2423bf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190206/bkn-20190206121210727-0206_00822_001.html</a>"}]}